text: Rosanna DeSoto (born September 2, 1950)Hollywood.com is an American actress. She is best known for her roles in Stand and Deliver, for which she won an Independent Spirit Award for Best Supporting Female, and in Star Trek VI: The Undiscovered Country as Azetbur. ==References== Category:1950 births Category:American movie actors Category:American television actors Category:American voice actors Category:Living people Category:Actors from California
